Package pl.polsl.mostowska.integrationwebapp.model

Class ResultsEntity

java.lang.Object
pl.polsl.mostowska.integrationwebapp.model.ResultsEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class ResultsEntity extends Object implements Serializable
Entity class representing the result of a numerical integration calculation. This class is used for storing the integration parameters and result in the database.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Wiktoria Mostowska
